<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <script defer src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script defer type="module" src="../../scripts/main.js"></script>
    <!-- <script defer src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script> -->
    <title>Remote Playground</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="bigcontainer">

        <header id="header">
            <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        </header>

    <div id="statuses-container">
        <section id="leader">
            <div id="leader-box"> <p id="leader-heading"><b>LeaderBoard: </b></p></div>
        </section>

        <section id="online-count">
            <div id="online-box"><p id="online"><b>Online: 0</b></p></div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <section id="playground" class="pad5percent">
        <h1 id="play-heading" class="textctr">PLAYGROUND</h1>
        <div id="play-chat-container">
            <div id="play-container">
                <!-- <div id="play-box"><img id="videoStream" src="/images/maintenance_logo.png"></div> -->
                <div id="play-box"><img id="videoStream" src="/stream.mjpg"></div> /* Comment if no RPI */
                    <div id="play-buttons">
                        <input id="simon-startquit" type="button" class="button" value="Start">
                        <input id="gpio0" type="button" class="button leds" value="LED0">
                        <input id="gpio1" type="button" class="button leds" value="LED1">
                        <input id="gpio2" type="button" class="button leds" value="LED2">
                        <input id="gpio3" type="button" class="button leds" value="LED3">
                    </div>
                </div>
            <div id="chat-container">
                <div id="chat-header-box">
                    <h1 id="chat-header">LIVE CHAT</h1>
                </div>
                <div id="chat-text-box">
                    <div id="text-box">
                    <ul>
                    </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div id="chat-input-con">
                    <input id="chat-input" placeholder="Type to Chat">
                    <input id="chatbutton" type="button" class="button" value="Send">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="pad5percent">
        <h1 id="about-heading">ABOUT</h1>
        <p>
            When we think about interactive entertainment, we commonly tend towards triple A games on the latest consoles, or live-streaming platforms like YouTube or Twitch as the premiere embodiments of interactive entertainment. <br><br> We aim to <u>REDEFINE</u> the limits of what interactive entertainment can be, by introducing a way for individuals to enact real-time physical changes through a few simple clicks on a website, while receiving real-time feedback on those very changes. <br><br> Hence, we hope to be the initial spark that <u>IGNITES</u> a new wave of interactive entertainment based on interfacing software-hardware at a user-friendly level, in order to provide the highest levels of entertainment for the <u>MASSES</u>.
        </p>
    </section>

